 a broad perspective of learning that prepares students to comprehend, connect, and collect marketable skills needed to become successful citizens and leaders in the community. The Core is designed, taught, and assessed by faculty members from the University of North Texas who work in concert to assure that students explore and learn from contact with faculty from multiple disciplines. Visit Us   Office of the Provost and VP for Academic Affairs370 Hurley Administration Building Mail Us   University of North TexasOffice of the Provost and VP for Academic Affairs 1155 Union Circle #311190 Denton, Texas 76203-5017 [map]   Contact Us   940-565-2550 TTY: 940-369-8652 FAX: 940-565-2774 For questions about this website, contact ronda.bewley@unt.edu   Site last updated on: May 09, 2017 Disclaimer  |  AA/EOE/ADA  |  Privacy  |   Electronic Accessibility  |  State of Texas Online  |  Emergency Preparedness  |  THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information  |  UNT Compliance Hotline  |  Governors Committee on People with Disabilities  |  Texas Veterans Portal  |  UNT Home 